thread.title: Stuffo Stuffo

author: Stuffo Stuffo
title: Stuffo Stuffo
text: I was at one of those box stores looking at printers. The one I liked wasn't on sale. The clerk said we may have an on line coupon, so I put the co. name and model number into my phone to check and found the printer I really wanted advertised by emmeco FOR 1/2 THE PRICE IT WAS LISTED FOR AT THE OTHER STORE. I promptly thanked the clerk walked out to my car and ordered the printer. I didn't think the printer would ship...the price was to good. I waited about a week for it to come, arriving in perfect condition, no hassle, no interaction NO COMPLAINTS and I got it for I/2 of what I almost paid.
